  <entry>
    <title>用caddy本地反代github</title>
    <link href="https://blog.crisipa.icu/2023/10/08/%E7%94%A8caddy%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8D%E4%BB%A3giyhub/"/>
    <id>https://blog.crisipa.icu/2023/10/08/%E7%94%A8caddy%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8D%E4%BB%A3giyhub/</id>
    <published>2023-10-08T02:54:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-10-08T14:23:40.366Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>github的网络问题已经是老生常谈的了。</p><h2 id="准备工具"><a href="#准备工具" class="headerlink" title="准备工具"></a>准备工具</h2><h3 id="下载caddy"><a href="#下载caddy" class="headerlink" title="下载caddy"></a>下载caddy</h3><p>caddy 是一个开源的跨平台服务器软件，旨在提供简单易用的配置和自动化的 HTTPS 功能。比起nginx，caddy的配置文件相当简洁</p><p>官网：<a href="https://caddyserver.com/">https://caddyserver.com/</a><br>下载链接：<a href="https://github.com/caddyserver/caddy/releases">https://github.com/caddyserver/caddy/releases</a> 或 <a href="https://caddyserver.com/download">https://caddyserver.com/download</a><br>文档：<a href="https://caddyserver.com/docs/">https://caddyserver.com/docs/</a></p><p>随便找个文件夹把它放进去</p><h3 id="安装openssl"><a href="#安装openssl" class="headerlink" title="安装openssl"></a>安装openssl</h3><p>先安装 openssl ,windows用户从这里下载：<a href="https://slproweb.com/products/Win32OpenSSL.html">https://slproweb.com/products/Win32OpenSSL.html</a></p><p>安装后记得配置下环境变量（Windows用户专属）：把openssl安装目录下的bin文件夹的路径加进path变量里</p><h2 id="制作原料"><a href="#制作原料" class="headerlink" title="制作原料"></a>制作原料</h2><h3 id="签个根证书"><a href="#签个根证书" class="headerlink" title="签个根证书"></a>签个根证书</h3><p>参考资料： <a href="https://2heng.xin/2018/12/16/your-own-ca-with-openssl/">https://2heng.xin/2018/12/16/your-own-ca-with-openssl/</a></p><h4 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h4><p>在你放caddy的文件夹里，新建一个txt文件 index.txt<br>然后在此目录里打开终端输入命令</p><figure class="highlight sas"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sas">openssl genrsa -<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> github.com.<span class="hljs-keyword">key</span> 2048<br>openssl genrsa -<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> rootCA.<span class="hljs-keyword">key</span> 2048<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="制作CA证书"><a href="#制作CA证书" class="headerlink" title="制作CA证书"></a>制作CA证书</h4><p>在你放caddy的文件夹里，新建一个txt文件 config_rootCA.txt 并写入以下内容</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini"><span class="hljs-section">[ req ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">default_bits</span>= <span class="hljs-number">2048</span><br><br><span class="hljs-attr">prompt</span>    = <span class="hljs-literal">no</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">distinguished_name</span>= req_distinguished_name<br><span class="hljs-attr">v3_extensions</span>= v3_ext<br><br><span class="hljs-section">[ req_distinguished_name ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">countryName</span>    = CN<br><span class="hljs-attr">organizationName</span>= GFW Foundation<br><span class="hljs-attr">commonName</span>    = Local Fake CA<br><br><span class="hljs-section">[ v3_ext ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">keyUsage</span>    = keyCertSign,cRLSign<br><span class="hljs-attr">basicConstraints</span>= CA:<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">subjectKeyIdentifier</span>= hash<br><span class="hljs-attr">authorityKeyIdentifier</span>= keyid,issuer<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在之前的终端里输入命令</p><figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs maxima">openssl req -<span class="hljs-built_in">new</span> -x509 -<span class="hljs-built_in">key</span> rootCA.<span class="hljs-built_in">key</span> -out rootCA.crt -days <span class="hljs-number">3650</span> -config config_rootCA.txt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="用这个CA证书签SSL证书"><a href="#用这个CA证书签SSL证书" class="headerlink" title="用这个CA证书签SSL证书"></a>用这个CA证书签SSL证书</h4><p>在你放caddy的文件夹里，再新建一个txt文件 config_childCA.txt 并写入以下内容</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini"><span class="hljs-section">[ req ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">default_bits</span>= <span class="hljs-number">2048</span><br><br><span class="hljs-attr">prompt</span>    = <span class="hljs-literal">no</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">distinguished_name</span>= req_distinguished_name<br><span class="hljs-attr">req_extensions</span>= v3_req<br><br><span class="hljs-section">[ req_distinguished_name ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">countryName</span>    = CN<br><span class="hljs-attr">organizationName</span>= GFW Foundation<br><span class="hljs-attr">commonName</span>    = LocalFakeCA<br><br><span class="hljs-section">[ alternate_names ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">DNS.01</span> = github.com<br><span class="hljs-attr">DNS.02</span> = *.github.com<br><span class="hljs-attr">DNS.03</span> = githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-attr">DNS.04</span> = *.githubusercontent.com<br><br><span class="hljs-section">[ v3_req ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">keyUsage</span>    = digitalSignature<br><span class="hljs-attr">extendedKeyUsage</span>= serverAuth,clientAuth<br><span class="hljs-attr">basicConstraints</span>= CA:<span class="hljs-literal">false</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">subjectAltName</span>= @alternate_names<br><span class="hljs-attr">subjectKeyIdentifier</span>    = hash<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在你放caddy的文件夹里，再新建一个txt文件 config_signCA.txt 并写入以下内容</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini"><span class="hljs-section">[ ca ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">default_ca</span>= myca<br><br><span class="hljs-section">[ myca ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">serial</span>    = ./crtserial.srl<br><span class="hljs-attr">database</span>    = ./index.txt<br><span class="hljs-attr">new_certs_dir</span>= ./<br><span class="hljs-attr">certificate</span>    = ./rootCA.crt<br><span class="hljs-attr">private_key</span>    = ./rootCA.key<br><span class="hljs-attr">default_md</span>    = sha256<br><span class="hljs-attr">default_days</span>= <span class="hljs-number">3650</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">unique_subject</span>= <span class="hljs-literal">no</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">policy</span>    = my_policy<br><span class="hljs-attr">copy_extensions</span>= copy<br><br><br><span class="hljs-section">[ my_policy ]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">countryName</span>    = optional<br><span class="hljs-attr">stateOrProvinceName</span>= optional<br><span class="hljs-attr">localityName</span>= optional<br><span class="hljs-attr">organizationName</span>= optional<br><span class="hljs-attr">organizationalUnitName</span>= optional<br><span class="hljs-attr">commonName</span>    = supplied<br><span class="hljs-attr">emailAddress</span>= optional<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在之前的终端里输入命令</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">echo <span class="hljs-number">01</span> &gt; crtserial<span class="hljs-selector-class">.srl</span><br>openssl req -new -sha256 -key github<span class="hljs-selector-class">.com</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.key</span> -out github<span class="hljs-selector-class">.com</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.csr</span> -config config_childCA<span class="hljs-selector-class">.txt</span><br>openssl ca -config config_signCA<span class="hljs-selector-class">.txt</span> -<span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> github<span class="hljs-selector-class">.com</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.csr</span> -out github<span class="hljs-selector-class">.com</span>.crt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="制作-Caddyfile"><a href="#制作-Caddyfile" class="headerlink" title="制作 Caddyfile"></a>制作 Caddyfile</h3><p>在你放caddy的文件夹里，新建一个txt文件 <a href="">Caddyfile</a> (没有后缀名) </p><p>先塞全局配置<br>其中最重要的就是 auto_https disable_certs 。若是省去，caddy会自动帮你申请证书。但是我们是要在本地进行反向代理，申请不了证书的。</p><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx">&#123;<br><span class="hljs-comment"># General Options</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">http_port</span>    <span class="hljs-number">80</span><br>https_port   <span class="hljs-number">443</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#default_bind &lt;host&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># TLS Options</span><br>    auto_https disable_certs<br>    admin <span class="hljs-literal">off</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后是对 github.com 的配置 </p><figure class="highlight dns"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dns">github.com &#123;<br>    tls .\github.com.crt .\github.com.key<br>    reverse_proxy &#123;<br>        to <span class="hljs-number">140.82.112.3</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 140.82</span>.<span class="hljs-number">112.4:443</span> <span class="hljs-number">140.82.113.3</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 140.82</span>.<span class="hljs-number">113.4:443</span><br>        lb_policy random<br>        fail_duration <span class="hljs-number">60</span>s  #失败时间<br>        max_fails <span class="hljs-number">60</span>       #失败计数<br>        unhealthy_status <span class="hljs-number">502 500</span> <span class="hljs-number">503 403</span><br>        flush_interval -<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>        header_up Host &#123;http.request.host&#125;<br>        transport http &#123;<br>tls<br>tls_insecure_skip_verify<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还有 raw 头像 静态资源 这些</p><figure class="highlight dns"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dns">githubusercontent.com *.githubusercontent.com raw.github.com &#123;<br>    tls .\github.com.crt .\github.com.key<br>    reverse_proxy &#123;<br>        to <span class="hljs-number">151.101.88.133</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 151.101</span>.<span class="hljs-number">196.133:443</span> <span class="hljs-number">151.101.40.133</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 151.164</span>.<span class="hljs-number">133:443 151</span>.<span class="hljs-number">101.24.133</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 151.101</span>.<span class="hljs-number">128.133:443</span> <span class="hljs-number">151.101.192.133</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 151.101</span>.<span class="hljs-number">120.133:443</span> <span class="hljs-number">151.101.64.133</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443</span><br>        lb_policy random<br>        fail_duration <span class="hljs-number">60</span>s  #失败时间<br>        max_fails <span class="hljs-number">60</span>       #失败计数<br>        unhealthy_status <span class="hljs-number">502 500</span> <span class="hljs-number">503 403</span><br>        flush_interval -<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>        header_up Host &#123;http.request.host&#125;<br>        transport http &#123;<br>tls<br>tls_insecure_skip_verify<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后是似乎没多大用的gist</p><figure class="highlight dns"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dns">gist.github.com &#123;<br>    tls .\github.com.crt .\github.com.key<br>    reverse_proxy &#123;<br>        to <span class="hljs-number">20.207.73.82</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 140.82</span>.<span class="hljs-number">113.3:443</span> <span class="hljs-number">140.82.121.4</span>:<span class="hljs-number">443 140.82</span>.<span class="hljs-number">121.3:443</span><br>        lb_policy random<br>        fail_duration <span class="hljs-number">60</span>s  #失败时间<br>        max_fails <span class="hljs-number">60</span>       #失败计数<br>        unhealthy_status <span class="hljs-number">502 500</span> <span class="hljs-number">503 403</span><br>        flush_interval -<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>        header_up Host &#123;http.request.host&#125;<br>        transport http &#123;<br>tls<br>tls_insecure_skip_verify<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>你还可以用这方式上steam :)</p><h2 id="启动"><a href="#启动" class="headerlink" title="启动"></a>启动</h2><p>直接在你放caddy的文件夹里开一个终端运行条命令就启动caddy了</p><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs applescript">./caddy <span class="hljs-built_in">run</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后修改hosts文件，加入这些：</p><figure class="highlight accesslog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs accesslog">## github<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> github.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> raw.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> cloud.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> camo.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> user-images.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> avatars3.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> avatars2.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> avatars1.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> avatars0.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> avatars.githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> raw.github.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> githubusercontent.com<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.1</span> gist.github.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>别忘了关闭git的ssl验证：</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> http<span class="hljs-selector-class">.sslverify</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;false&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>好了，github的使用体验应该已经得到了改善</p><h2 id="一些问题"><a href="#一些问题" class="headerlink" title="一些问题"></a>一些问题</h2><h3 id="1-ssh用不了"><a href="#1-ssh用不了" class="headerlink" title="1.ssh用不了"></a>1.ssh用不了</h3><p>个人技术有限，而且也不是必须用ssh： <a href="https://docs.github.com/zh/get-started/getting-started-with-git/caching-your-github-credentials-in-git">https://docs.github.com/zh/get-started/getting-started-with-git/caching-your-github-credentials-in-git</a></p><h3 id="2-白屏或502"><a href="#2-白屏或502" class="headerlink" title="2.白屏或502"></a>2.白屏或502</h3><p>多试几次就行了</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
        
        
